lead_paragraph: UNRRA's three weeks' session at Atlantic City, just concluded, hasn't had the dramatic aspects of a conference of heads of Governments. Under the director-generalship of former Gov. Herbert H. Lehman international relief and rehabilitation is not likely to display fireworks.
